arty.\n\nDespite coming closer on some major issues, including the decision to nominate NCP Vice Chairman Bamdev Gautam to the National Assembly, the party leadership is caught in a dispute on issues regarding the supposed cabinet reshuffle, and Chief Ministers.\n\nParty insiders say that the leadership is reluctant to address the recommendations of the task force.\n\nLikewise, Dahal and Oli are also likely to discuss the appointment of two ministers \u2013 Minister of Communication and Information, and Minister of Finance \u2013 after the resignation of the then Finance Minister Dr Yubaraj Khatiwada.","title":"Dahal-Oli meeting underway at Baluwatar - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/09/126142/","video":[]}
